 asa flow to yin practice ending in savasana. Join our community and meet o
 ther like-minded people! Yoga heals. Nature heals. Yoga In Nature™.\n\nP
 ractice vinyasa flow to yin yoga at North Carolina Museum of Art\, outdoor
 s near upper parking area in grass ellipse... (NOTE THIS GRASS LOCATION\, 
 as there are other groups that use NCMA grounds). WHEN YOU COME INTO THE P
 ARKING LOT\, DRIVE TO WHERE THE TWO PARKING LOTS ON BLUE RIDGE MEET\, AWAY
