 h\nVenmo @Darlene-Genander (0862)\nPaypal dgenander@yogainnature.com\nZell
 e\n\nCome flow with us. Meet others and make friends in our yoga community
 .\nBring a mat\; water\; and anything else you may need for your outdoor y
