SUMMARY:"Women Together" Yoga & Wellness (Spring) Retreat
DESCRIPTION:Yoga In Nature™\, NC\n**Payment of $115 due at signup to hol
 d your spot. Limited to 10 women.**\nA retreat created for YOU to come and
  rest\, play\, experience who you are away from responsibilities of your d
 aily life. Drop into nature and the season of Spring at Sky Pond with all 
 things in bloom and the opportunity to **'Root to Rise'** (theme) in your 
 yoga practice and to claim what is next in your journey of life😊\n\n* v
 inyasa flow to yin yoga and meditation (open to all levels and beginners)\
 ; practice will be outdoors unless rain then we will practice indoors in y
 oga studio\n* nature immersion and nature walk\; mandala creation\n* conne
 ctions and conversations with other women who share similar interests\n* g
 uided journaling\; reading\; coloring\; creating\n* snacks\; light nourish
 ing lunch\; seasonal hot and/or cold teas\n* wellness gift to support your
  growth journey\n\nArrival at 8:45am and feel free to stay beyond the prog
 ram time of 1:30\, until 2pm to enjoy the space.\n$115/person due at signu
 p to hold your spot\nPayable by Venmo @Darlene-Genander (0862 if asked)\; 
 PayPal dgenander@yogainnature\; Zelle
